Since 2011, Global Citizen has recorded over 19 million shares from its supporters, who are advocating for many different goals.
According to the organization, these actions have helped to inspire world leaders to make commitments and adopt policies worth more than $37 billion that are expected to change the lives of more than 2.25 billion people by 2030.
